{"tid":469323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"衝浪遇見大白鯊　英國醫生一拳打跑牠","createTime":"2017-11-15T07:50:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-17T12:10:51.000Z","uid":13468,"like":323,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"22a9d0cd6916d3cb67599aaa3b74048cfa89e5de","tid":469323,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T07:50:05.000Z","msg":"衝浪遇見大白鯊　英國醫生一拳打跑牠<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171114/1240923/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171114%2F1240923%2F&d=ywWURTQq08Fzn72WMUz%2FuaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=6ddf9258\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171114%2F1240923%2F&h=ced74e88\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171114/1240923/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171114/640_b7955f360af82a44ad40751da4fa113f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171114%2F640_b7955f360af82a44ad40751da4fa113f.jpg&h=5554e7f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一名英國籍醫生昨日下午在澳洲衝浪時遭3米長「大白鯊」襲擊，靠拳打鯊魚鼻逃離鯊口。<br />\n<br />\n25歲的弗賴伊（Charlie Fry）在雪梨以北阿沃卡海灘（Avoca Beach）衝浪時遇襲，右肩和上臂被咬傷。<br />\n <br />\n弗賴伊今日接受電視台訪問，說當時他與3名醫生朋友衝浪，感到身體右邊被重擊，形容當時被「殺個措手不及」。鯊魚頭露出水面朝他狠咬，他用左手揮拳打向鯊魚鼻，逃脫後再爬回衝浪板，返回岸邊，由朋友送醫。弗賴伊說，當時只知自己幾乎喪命，上岸才發現手臂受傷流血。<br />\n <br />\n弗賴伊說，最近上YouTube看過澳洲衝浪好手芬寧（Mick Fanning）的影片，當中他說2015年在南非比賽時，曾揮拳擊退一隻大白鯊而逃過一劫，於是有樣學樣，結果成功保命，表示會請芬寧喝啤酒。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"0c7f1a7206b5839c2df416ec74462fad5c3d43cd","tid":469323,"uid":47775,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T07:51:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd887d74a5e2cede961f9a1f32af566c84e20334","tid":469323,"uid":119494,"like":34,"dislike":3,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"repl